{"questionId":"11769","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>It is believed that two variables, <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"m\">\n  <mi>m</mi>\n</math></span> and <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"p\">\n  <mi>p</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp;are related. Experimental values of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"m\">\n  <mi>m</mi>\n</math></span> and&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"p\">\n  <mi>p</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp;are obtained. A graph of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{ln}}\\,m\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>ln</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>m</mi>\n</math></span> against <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"p\">\n  <mi>p</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp;shows a straight line passing through (2.1, 7.3) and (5.6, 2.4).</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Hence, find</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>the value of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"m\">\n  <mi>m</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp;when <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"p = 0\">\n  <mi>p</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>28000&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[1 mark]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"11769","referenceCode":"EXM.1.AHL.TZ0.13b.ii","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"the value of m when p = 0 .","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"b.ii","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 2—Functions","Topic 2—Functions","AHL 2.10—Scaling large numbers, log-log graphs"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}